Input: data file
Export:  PDF plots, 
        Excel workbook with:
          - master summary sheet
          - monthly sheets

"proximity_flag": abs(r_pearson) > R_FLAG_THRESHOLD or abs(r_spearman) > R_FLAG_THRESHOLD,
          R_FLAG_THRESHOLD = 0.5 

5 minute bins 

50% coverage 

tag_id = Motus tag ID
receiver = Receiver/station name
month = Year-month
n_bins = Number of valid daytime 5-min bins
mean_sig = Mean signal strength across bins
mean_bin_std = Mean within-bin signal standard deviation
r_pearson = Pearson correlation between mean signal and std dev (parametric) 
r_squared_pearson = Pearson (r^2)
r_spearman = Spearman rank correlation
divergence = Absolute difference between Pearson and Spearman
slope = OLS regression slope
intercept = OLS regression intercept
Proximity_flag = if correlation is too high (TRUE) 
Coverage pct = fraction of the month that had valid bins


